description.text: Indulge in luxury living with this top-floor penthouse condo, boasting 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, updated kitchen, and baths, and living spaces with modern finishes, rich laminate wood flooring and high ceilings that enhance the feeling of space and openness!. Enjoy magnificent views from the massive patio and airy roof deck. These spaces are ideal for entertaining and taking advantage of the gorgeous Los Angeles weather! Enjoy the comfort of central a/c and convenience of a full size laundry room with side by side washer/dryer and extra storage. Gated parking with EV chargers and guest parking too. Centrally located adjacent to Larchmont Village and Melrose Hill. Walkable neighborhood with nearby trendy caf's (Le Coupe, Organico, Ggiata, and Sweet Corner Coffee) This condo is the epitome of sophistication and convenience, waiting for you to make it your own. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity for exquisite city living!
